    <worksheet name='Regional Loss vs Sales (Tables)'>
      <layout-options>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11'>East = Highest Financial Damage</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>“The East region contributes the highest absolute losses in the Tables category (~$11K), despite generating substantial sales, indicating a volume-driven profitability issue where a large number of transactions are loss-making.”</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11'>South = Moderate Risk</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>“The South region shows moderate losses with comparatively lower sales, suggesting a contained but still inefficient pricing structure.”</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11'>Central = Hidden Risk </run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>“Although Central does not contribute the highest absolute loss, it demonstrates significant margin erosion when combined with discount analysis, indicating inefficiency in pricing strategy rather than scale.”</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11'>West = Only Profitable Region</run>
            <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='11' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>“The West region is the only region generating positive profit while maintaining the highest sales volume, indicating effective pricing and discount management.”</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='Sheet1 (SuperStore Sales DataSet)' name='federated.0851brr08q3wbf1h5glde00p5wbj' />
          </datasources>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='federated.0851brr08q3wbf1h5glde00p5wbj'>
            <column caption='Total Loss' datatype='real' default-format='c&quot;$&quot;#,##0.00' name='[Calculation_0497865268953089]' role='measure' type='quantitative'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='SUM(IF [Loss Making Sub-Categories] THEN [Profit] END)' />
            </column>
            <column caption='CalcLoss Indicator' datatype='string' name='[Calculation_0497865303465986]' role='measure' type='nominal'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='IF [Calculation_0497865268953089] &lt; 0 THEN &quot;Loss&quot; ELSE &quot;Profit&quot; END' />
            </column>
            <column caption='Profit Indicator' datatype='string' name='[Calculation_1962419065569281]' role='measure' type='nominal'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='IF SUM([Profit]) &lt; 0 THEN &quot;Loss&quot;&#13;&#10;ELSE &quot;Profit&quot;&#13;&#10;END' />
            </column>
            <column datatype='real' name='[Profit]' role='measure' type='quantitative' />
            <column datatype='string' name='[Region]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column datatype='real' name='[Sales]' role='measure' type='quantitative' />
            <column datatype='string' name='[Sub-Category]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[Region]' derivation='None' name='[none:Region:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[Sub-Category]' derivation='None' name='[none:Sub-Category:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[Profit]' derivation='Sum' name='[sum:Profit:qk]' pivot='key' type='quantitative' />
            <column-instance column='[Sales]' derivation='Sum' name='[sum:Sales:qk]' pivot='key' type='quantitative' />
            <column-instance column='[Calculation_0497865303465986]' derivation='User' name='[usr:Calculation_0497865303465986:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
