          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Times New Roman' fontsize='12'>The profitability issue in the Tables category is primarily driven by excessive discounting, where revenue is being generated at the expense of margins. Without enforcing discount thresholds and optimizing pricing strategy, continued sales growth will lead to further financial leakage rather than value creation.</run>
